Package io.github.zero88.schedulerx

Interface JobData<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of data
public interface JobData<T>
Represents for a provider that supplies input data before the execution is started, and that will be sent to the job in runtime execution.
Since:
1.0.0

    • get

      @Nullable T get()
      Get an input data.

      It might be a static input value or a preloaded value from an external system or a configuration to instruct how to get actual input data of the job in runtime execution.

    • externalId

      @Nullable default @Nullable Object externalId()
      Declares a unique id in an external system that will be propagated to the job result.

      That makes the integration between the job monitoring and the external system seamless and easier.

      Returns:
      an external id
